Rahul Goel, MRC Epidemiology Unit, University of Cambridge, UK

25 April 2019

Introduction

These are the summary tables of the following items 1) Individual-level PM2.5 concentrations for baseline and scenarios 2) Individual-level physical activity for baseline and scenarios 3) Distance mode shares for baseline and scenarios
